summary: The St. Catharines Saints is a senior ice hockey club in the Allan Cup Hockey League (ACH) based in St. Catharines, Ontario.
biography: The St. Catharines Saints is a senior ice hockey club in the Allan Cup Hockey League (ACH) based in St. Catharines, Ontario. The club plays its home games at the Merritton Centennial Arena in St. Catharines.
